Source.Name: python-asn1-modules
Source.Summary: A collection of ASN.1-based protocols modules
Source.Description: A collection of ASN.1 modules expressed in form of pyasn1 classes. Includes protocols PDUs definition (SNMP, LDAP etc.) and various data structures (X.509, PKCS etc.).
